dcterms:description: This dataset contains 2700 videos of various lengths. They were captured in outdoor environments so issues, such as tree waving, camera shaking, noise, illumination changes, and rain, are common. Some videos have human motion also. The outdoor scenes include car parks, train stations, bus stops, etc.
dcterms:title: iCetanaPrivateDataset

dcterms:description: This dataset is an extension of iCetanaPrivateDataset, with videos captured by multiple cameras located at different train stations, bus stops, moving lifts, restaurants, and supermarkets. It has 6668 videos.
dcterms:title: iCetanaEventDataset
